OL,3,CPolice warning as potentially
OL,4,C'hazardous' smoke spreads from farm
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,FPeople living near the scene of a farm
OL,8,Ffire in North Somerset have been told
OL,9,Fto keep their doors and windows closed.
OL,11,FAvon and Somerset Police say smoke
OL,12,Ffrom the blaze at Chestnut Farm near
OL,13,FClaverham may contain hazardous
OL,14,Fchemicals. An 800metre cordon has been
OL,15,Ferected around the site.
OL,17,FIt was first reported just before
OL,18,F9.20pm on Saturday 2 August and crews
OL,19,Ffrom Avon Fire and Rescue Service
OL,20,Fremain at the scene.
