OL,7,FPolice say no injuries have been
OL,8,Freported but they're assisting the
OL,9,Ffire service with road closures and
OL,10,Fthe South Western Ambulance Service
OL,11,Fare also in attendance.
OL,13,FA spokesperson added: "Unless
OL,14,Fotherwise instructed by emergency
OL,15,Fpersonnel, residents within 800 metres
OL,16,Fof the farm should stay inside, with
OL,17,Fdoors and windows closed as a
OL,18,Fprecaution against smoke which may
OL,19,Fcontain hazardous chemicals.
